text: Mirosław Zenon Jarzembowski (born 20 February 1954) is a Polish rower. He competed in the men's coxless four event at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1954 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Poland Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bydgoszcz
